{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">TUTORIAL&amp;HINT: A manual is prepared for you in case you need some help. You can find it on the right column of your steam client library. </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DESCRIPTION</h2><strong>The Drained Goddess</strong> is a first-person survival horror game  achieved with CryEngine. It focuses on combat system and side story exploration. You will need to fight with many unique enemies and investigate the twisted fate of our main character. Finally you can put different endings to the story.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1265650/extras/DryZombieAppear.gif?t=1650633446\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Rich Enemies</h2>There are many unique featured enemies. Their behaviors and abilities are specialized.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1265650/extras/thrown_white_phosphorus.gif?t=1650633446\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Rich Equipment</h2>You can get various unique equipment during the game, including melee weapons, thrown and magic spells. They have different attack styles and damage types.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1265650/extras/SwordAndFireAttack_DriedLady.gif?t=1650633446\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Exploration</h2>Most enemies are optional to fight with or even triggered. Some side stories will affect story endings.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1265650/extras/Timeline_DoctorAttack.gif?t=1650633446\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Flexible Difficulty Levels</h2>Puzzles and enemies in side stories are more difficult to deal with in general. Also you probably don't have enough resources to fight with all enemies easily. This will provide different experiences.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1265650/extras/YinChai_Attack.gif?t=1650633446\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Breaker","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1265650/fc757d0b1c1511e53369c524924f426323ebb0ea.jpg"},{"name":"Extermination","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1265650/3abbe9b4524ed6366ebb692d8f3c365d6e804f6a.jpg"},{"name":"Full of Echoes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1265650/2ff079d79192d8bae2408d4d2ebb8a520db3ead3.jpg"},{"name":"Nightmare","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1265650/8daa9f2eae64e0c46f5cf54701469fe8614e1cba.jpg"},{"name":"Thousands Miles Away","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1265650/b6e0e9ee0fae9b2a7b7708205257f637fe3544d4.jpg"},{"name":"Hometown","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1265650/6d1149691120b3a3f20fe54ebfc7aefcbbaba3c0.jpg"},{"name":"See No Evil","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1265650/95fd46e923f2ec8a48e39b7d55c54d6710e3d5ff.jpg"},{"name":"Wasp","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1265650/0de42c08652e0067c9a442194bfdaaddf0861d06.jpg"},{"name":"Gardening","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1265650/60ab9764d5fabc992cf42f47a476ccd599081825.jpg"},{"name":"Sick","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1265650/7b7fe66c0ed0496a5972b1a3126b363236e5b881.jpg"}],"total":32},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1265650/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1650633446","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1265650/page.bg.jpg?t=1650633446","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1265650/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1650633446","capsule_imagev5":"http